### Phase 3: 安全區處理 (低優先)

#### 修改 [PathPlanningTracker.cs](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs)
```csharp
public PointF? GetNearestSafeZone(PointF playerPos)
{
    if (_safeZones == null || _safeZones.Count == 0)
        return null;
    
    return _safeZones
        .OrderBy(z => Distance(playerPos, z))
        .FirstOrDefault();
}

// 當血量低時，優先前往安全區
public void OnLowHealth()
{
    var safeZone = GetNearestSafeZone(CurrentPlayerPosition);
    if (safeZone.HasValue)
    {
        SetTemporaryTarget(safeZone.Value, priority: high);
    }
}
```

